room_title: Escape room "The Spirited Study" by 1863 Escape in Gettysburg
review: We had a terrific time in the Spirited Study! The hour flew by - all 6 of us were very busy! Good job on the set up!!

room_title: Escape room "The Spirited Study" by 1863 Escape in Gettysburg
review: So much fun for all ages! Our group of 3 teamed up with another group of 3. Together we escaped The Spirited Study. The clues were well thought out and the staff was super friendly! Check this place out! You won't be disappointed.
